txt.en: Bálach Iaran, the Iron Pass can be found in west Câr Bronach.\n\nYou should lay traps at the Iron Pass for Suilgál.

'If Soltakh trusts you enough to assist us, then I will give you a task.\n\n'You will find some traps over there in a chest. Fetch them, then set them upon the steps of Bálach Iaran, The Iron Pass. We must do what we can to thwart any loyal to the Iron Crown from entering Câr Bronach.'
'You have done well, [placeholder]. I am pleased with your efforts.'
